All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    A class that represents a board using a set of Location objects.
    Knight
    The Knight class is a subclass of the abstract Piece class, implementing movement logic for a Knight chess piece.
    Location
    A class that represents a location using a pair of integer coordinates (x, y).
    Piece
    A chess piece abstract base class that extends the Location class and requires methods for implementing necessary movement logic.
    Tour
    A class that determines the moves a chess piece should make, such that it lands on every square of a board once.
    TourViewer
    A class that simulates a Tour and draws it using the StdDraw library.
